This rock relief is situated on the east of Jahan Abad-1, lies in the middle of orchard of apple. It reveals a [[Avalokiteśvara]] in [https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lalitasana lalitasana] in pensive mood of a high seat. His right hand rests on his right, while his left one on his right, while his left one his thigh holding a lotus flower (full-blown). He wears a prominent head-dress and a necklace. The rock has thick layer of patina, which made the much of the details illegible.

